==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Atrip
<hw>A*trip"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>trip</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>Just hove clear of the ground; -- said of the anchor.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>Sheeted home, hoisted taut up and ready for trimming;
-- said of sails.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>Hoisted up and ready to be
swayed across; -- said of yards.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Atriplex</ent>⟦br⟧
